# Coalesce author/committer identities into one canonical GitHub identity.
# Display-only (git shortlog/log/blame + GitHub contributor view); does NOT
# rewrite history. dependabot[bot] is intentionally left untouched.
# The trailing-email mappings are load-bearing: they fold older commit-author
# addresses into the canonical no-reply identity in the contributor view.
# Removing them would surface those raw addresses on historical commits, so they
# stay until a (separate) history rewrite normalizes author metadata at the source.
